Package org.springframework.xd.analytics.ml.pmml

Package core abstractions for PMML support.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PmmlLoader
    Implementations are able to load a PMML from a given modelLocation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPmmlLoader
    An abstract implementation of a PmmlLoader that can build a PMML instance form a given InputSource.
    AnalyticPmmlProcessorOptionsMetadata
    Captures module options to the analytic-pmml module.
    AssociationTuplePmmlAnalyticOutputDataMapper
    An TuplePmmlAnalyticOutputDataMapper that can map the output of a PMML model evaluation of an Association model to a Tuple.
    PmmlAnalytic<I,O>
    A MappedAnalytic that can evaluate PMML models.
    ResourcePmmlLoader
    An AbstractPmmlLoader that can load PMML documents from a modelLocation given as resource URI.
    TuplePmmlAnalytic
    A PmmlAnalytic that works with Tuples.
    TuplePmmlAnalyticInputDataMapper
    An InputMapper that can map the Tuple to a to an appropriate input for a PMML model evaluation.
    TuplePmmlAnalyticOutputDataMapper
    An OutputMapper that can map the output of a PMML model evaluation to a Tuple.
